rows.label: qst201823_msg0005
rows.name:
Some days I thought
I'd never make it home again...

rows.label: qst201823_msg0006
rows.name:
I can't tell you how happy I am!
And how grateful, to Pepe and you both!

rows.label: qst201823_msg0007
rows.name:
No way, no way...
I didn't do anything special!

rows.label: qst201823_msg0008
rows.name:
Hey, let's not talk out here.
Come on, you're welcome inside!

rows.label: qst201823_msg0009
rows.name:
We should celebrate this, this...
this combination homecoming slash
heroic triumph!
